WEBVTT

00:00.667 --> 00:03.569
<i>♪ (peaceful)</i>

00:03.571 --> 00:12.711
<i>♪</i>

00:12.713 --> 00:15.114
Seems like only yesterday
I was saving this place

00:15.116 --> 00:16.615
From being totally destroyed.

00:16.617 --> 00:18.150
Hey, you guys remember that?

00:20.653 --> 00:24.423
You only mentioned it about
15 times on the train here.

00:24.425 --> 00:28.394
Yes, and we never hear a peep
out of you about your exploits.

00:28.396 --> 00:30.662
Heh heh. Point taken.

00:30.664 --> 00:32.431
I'm glad you all wanted to come,

00:32.433 --> 00:34.767
But I don't think it's
going to be that exciting.

00:34.769 --> 00:36.769
I pretty much just
have to smile and wave

00:36.771 --> 00:41.540
Yes, but you get to smile
and wave like a princess.

00:41.542 --> 00:44.176
How exactly is that different
than smiling and waving

00:44.178 --> 00:46.245
Like, not a princess?

00:47.380 --> 00:48.547
It isn't.

00:50.750 --> 00:52.484
What's wrong, twilight?

00:52.486 --> 00:56.655
Why the long face?

00:56.657 --> 00:59.258
I've just been feeling a little
unsure about things lately.

00:59.260 --> 01:01.427
It doesn't seem that my
new role as a princess

01:01.429 --> 01:02.661
Equates to all that much.

01:02.663 --> 01:06.331
You've got a real important
role in equestria.

01:06.333 --> 01:08.567
Princess celestia wouldn't have
asked you to come today

01:08.569 --> 01:10.369
If she didn't think so.

01:10.371 --> 01:12.137
I guess you're right.

01:12.139 --> 01:13.505
Of course we are.

01:13.507 --> 01:19.445
Diminished because you're tardy
for your regal meet and greet.

01:21.314 --> 01:23.415
<i>♪ (fanfare)</i>

01:23.417 --> 01:26.118
The duke and duchess
of mare-tonia.

01:26.120 --> 01:27.719
<i>♪ (processional)</i>

01:27.721 --> 01:39.698
♪

01:48.708 --> 01:50.776
<i>Spike: That was it?</i>

01:50.778 --> 01:52.744
Princess celestia had
you come all the way

01:52.746 --> 01:55.280
To the crystal empire
just to do that?

01:57.550 --> 02:00.185
I mean, whoa, really
regal and important!

02:00.187 --> 02:01.620
<i>(nervous laugh)</i>

02:01.622 --> 02:02.754
<i>(smack)</i>

02:07.594 --> 02:10.462
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

02:10.464 --> 02:12.464
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

02:12.466 --> 02:15.667
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

02:15.669 --> 02:17.836
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

02:17.838 --> 02:19.771
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

02:19.773 --> 02:22.174
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

02:22.176 --> 02:23.175
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

02:23.177 --> 02:25.444
<i>♪ a beautiful heart</i>

02:25.446 --> 02:30.649
<i>♪ and magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete ♪</i>

02:30.651 --> 02:32.718
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

02:32.720 --> 02:35.721
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

02:35.723 --> 02:38.857
♪

02:43.897 --> 02:47.766
<i>(echoing hoof sounds)</i>

02:47.768 --> 02:49.268
<i>(door opens)</i>

02:51.639 --> 02:55.207
Thank you for understanding our
desire to keep the number

02:55.209 --> 02:56.608
Of those privy to these
confidential discussions

02:56.610 --> 02:57.609
To a minimum.

02:57.611 --> 02:59.411
Of course.

03:04.817 --> 03:06.618
<i>(door closes)</i>

03:06.620 --> 03:11.290
Is there anything else I can
do to assist with their visit?

03:11.292 --> 03:14.526
I'm sorry, twilight, but
their visit is already over.

03:14.528 --> 03:15.627
Oh.

03:15.629 --> 03:19.898
I guess I just don't really
understand why I'm here.

03:19.900 --> 03:22.534
Couldn't one of the royal guard
have unfurled the banner?

03:22.536 --> 03:24.903
Having all four of us in
the empire to greet them

03:24.905 --> 03:26.605
Lets the dignitaries
know that their visit

03:26.607 --> 03:28.640
Is considered an important one.

03:28.642 --> 03:30.676
Plus, it gives me
an opportunity

03:30.678 --> 03:33.212
To see my favorite
sister-in-law.

03:33.214 --> 03:34.713
And I'm happy to see you.

03:34.715 --> 03:35.847
All of you.

03:38.484 --> 03:39.484
But...

03:39.486 --> 03:43.689
<i>Well, it's just that princess</i>
<i>luna raises the moon.</i>

03:43.691 --> 03:46.291
<i>Princess celestia</i>
<i>raises the sun.</i>

03:46.293 --> 03:48.527
You protect the crystal empire.

03:48.529 --> 03:50.429
And all I seem to do is...

03:50.431 --> 03:52.531
Smile and wave.

03:52.533 --> 04:01.540
♪

04:01.542 --> 04:04.576
♪ it isn't that I'm ungrateful

04:04.578 --> 04:05.944
<i>♪ for all the things</i>

04:05.946 --> 04:07.479
<i>♪ that I've earned</i>

04:07.481 --> 04:12.651
<i>♪ for all the journeys</i>
<i>I have taken ♪</i>

04:12.653 --> 04:16.388
<i>♪ all the lessons that</i>
<i>I have learned ♪</i>

04:16.390 --> 04:20.325
<i>♪ but I wonder where</i>
<i>I'm going now ♪</i>

04:20.327 --> 04:24.630
♪ what my role is meant to be

04:24.632 --> 04:28.267
<i>♪ I don't know how to travel</i>

04:28.269 --> 04:31.536
♪ to a future that I can't see

04:31.538 --> 04:38.944
<i>♪</i>

04:38.946 --> 04:40.479
<i>♪ I have my wings</i>

04:40.481 --> 04:42.481
<i>♪ I wear this crown</i>

04:42.483 --> 04:45.050
♪ I'm a princess this is true

04:45.052 --> 04:47.019
♪

04:47.021 --> 04:49.955
<i>♪ but it's still</i>
<i>unclear to me ♪</i>

04:49.957 --> 04:53.358
<i>♪ just what I am meant to do</i>

04:53.360 --> 04:54.760
<i>♪</i>

04:54.762 --> 04:58.030
<i>♪ I want to have a purpose</i>

04:58.032 --> 05:01.967
<i>♪ want to do all that I can</i>

05:01.969 --> 05:05.637
<i>♪ I want to make</i>
<i>a contribution ♪</i>

05:05.639 --> 05:09.541
<i>♪ I want to feel part</i>
<i>of the plan ♪</i>

05:09.543 --> 05:12.544
♪

05:12.546 --> 05:15.647
<i>♪ your destiny's uncertain</i>

05:15.649 --> 05:19.451
<i>♪ and that's sometimes</i>
<i>hard to take ♪</i>

05:19.453 --> 05:22.854
<i>♪ but it will become</i>
<i>much clearer ♪</i>

05:22.856 --> 05:26.858
<i>♪ with every new</i>
<i>choice you make ♪</i>

05:26.860 --> 05:30.362
<i>♪ patience is never easy</i>

05:30.364 --> 05:34.333
<i>♪ I understand</i>
<i>wanting more ♪</i>

05:34.335 --> 05:37.769
<i>♪ I know how hard</i>
<i>it is to wait ♪</i>

05:37.771 --> 05:41.907
<i>♪ to spread your</i>
<i>wings and soar ♪</i>

05:41.909 --> 05:44.910
<i>♪ but you stand</i>
<i>here for a reason ♪</i>

05:44.912 --> 05:48.714
<i>♪ you are gifted</i>
<i>and you are strong ♪</i>

05:48.716 --> 05:51.049
♪ that crown is upon your head

05:51.051 --> 05:55.420
<i>♪ because you belong</i>

05:55.422 --> 05:57.689
<i>♪ know that your time</i>

05:57.691 --> 05:59.358
<i>♪ is coming soon</i>

05:59.360 --> 06:00.892
<i>♪ as the sun rises</i>

06:00.894 --> 06:02.794
<i>♪ so does the moon</i>

06:02.796 --> 06:04.429
<i>♪ as love finds a place</i>

06:04.431 --> 06:06.598
<i>♪ in every heart</i>

06:06.600 --> 06:08.834
<i>♪ you are a princess</i>

06:08.836 --> 06:11.570
<i>♪ you'll play your part</i>

06:11.572 --> 06:14.873
<i>♪ we understand</i>
<i>you wanting more ♪</i>

06:14.875 --> 06:16.141
<i>♪ a chance to shine</i>

06:16.143 --> 06:18.844
<i>♪ a chance to soar</i>

06:18.846 --> 06:25.117
<i>♪ soon will come the</i>
<i>day it turns around ♪</i>

06:25.119 --> 06:28.653
<i>♪ know that your time</i>
<i>is coming soon ♪</i>

06:28.655 --> 06:30.489
<i>♪ as the sun rises</i>

06:30.491 --> 06:32.057
<i>♪ so does the moon</i>

06:32.059 --> 06:33.692
<i>♪ as love finds a place</i>

06:33.694 --> 06:35.894
<i>♪ in every heart</i>

06:35.896 --> 06:38.130
<i>♪ you are a princess</i>

06:38.132 --> 06:43.435
<i>♪ you'll play your part</i>

06:43.437 --> 06:45.737
<i>♪ you are a princess</i>

06:45.739 --> 06:50.842
<i>♪ you'll play your part</i>

06:53.946 --> 06:55.814
Your time will come.

06:55.816 --> 07:07.426
♪

07:07.428 --> 07:09.861
<i>♪ (scary)</i>

07:09.863 --> 07:12.864
♪

07:12.866 --> 07:13.999
<i>(clatter)</i>

07:15.501 --> 07:15.901
<i>(clatter)</i>

07:20.473 --> 07:22.941
<i>(heavy breathing)</i>

07:22.943 --> 07:24.075
Very sorry.

07:24.077 --> 07:25.710
You came out of nowhere.

07:27.213 --> 07:34.152
Is he friend or is he
foe, the pony wonders.

07:34.154 --> 07:35.954
I can assure you.

07:35.956 --> 07:39.591
I am no "friend".

07:39.593 --> 07:43.528
I am lord tirek.

07:43.530 --> 07:47.232
And I will take what should
have been mine long ago.

07:47.234 --> 07:55.574
<i>(whoosh)</i>

07:55.576 --> 07:57.509
<i>(thud)</i>

08:03.483 --> 08:05.484
<i>(evil laugh)</i>

08:07.487 --> 08:08.987
<i>(frightened gasps)</i>

08:08.989 --> 08:10.822
Sister, are you all right?

08:10.824 --> 08:13.558
I've just had the
most terrible dream.

08:13.560 --> 08:15.527
Why do you think I'm here?

08:15.529 --> 08:19.097
You know as well as I that this
was not a dream, but a vision.

08:19.099 --> 08:25.103
The stronger he becomes, the
more we are all in danger.

08:32.645 --> 08:36.281
♪

08:36.283 --> 08:38.717
<i>Celestia: Tirek and his</i>
<i>brother scorpan came here</i>

08:38.719 --> 08:42.554
<i>From a distant land, intent on</i>
<i>stealing equestrian magic.</i>

08:42.556 --> 08:44.890
<i>But scorpan soon came to</i>
<i>appreciate the ways</i>

08:44.892 --> 08:48.827
<i>Of equestria, even befriending</i>
<i>a young unicorn wizard.</i>

08:48.829 --> 08:51.963
Luna: Scorpan urged his brother
<i>to abandon their plans.</i>

08:51.965 --> 08:54.232
<i>When tirek refused,</i>
<i>scorpan alerted us</i>

08:54.234 --> 08:56.101
<i>To tirek's intentions.</i>

08:56.103 --> 08:58.703
<i>Celestia: Scorpan</i>
<i>returned to his own land,</i>

08:58.705 --> 09:01.873
<i>And tirek was sent to</i>
<i>tartarus for his crimes.</i>

09:01.875 --> 09:05.277
But it appears he has
found a way to escape.

09:05.279 --> 09:07.212
We believe it happened
when cerberus

09:07.214 --> 09:09.314
Left his post at
the gates.

09:09.316 --> 09:11.249
But that was a long time ago.

09:11.251 --> 09:13.852
Why is he just now
starting to steal magic?

09:13.854 --> 09:16.588
His time in tartarus
left him very weak.

09:16.590 --> 09:20.559
He has just now gained enough
strength to use his dark powers.

09:20.561 --> 09:23.828
But with each passing moment,
he grows stronger still.

09:23.830 --> 09:26.665
And I know just the
princess who could stop him.

09:26.667 --> 09:28.066
Yes! I'll find him and--

09:28.068 --> 09:32.971
I'm afraid I must call on
another to stop tirek.

09:32.973 --> 09:34.205
Discord.

09:34.207 --> 09:35.607
<i>(gasp)</i>

09:35.609 --> 09:38.176
As in discord, discord?

09:38.178 --> 09:41.980
I don't think it's
that big of a surprise.

09:41.982 --> 09:43.815
He can be very helpful.

09:46.018 --> 09:48.186
He can sense when there's a
magical imbalance.

09:48.188 --> 09:49.921
The next time
tirek steals magic,

09:49.923 --> 09:51.990
Discord will be able
to track him down.

09:51.992 --> 09:54.626
So what are you supposed
to do in the meantime?

09:54.628 --> 09:56.695
(sigh) nothing.

09:56.697 --> 09:59.364
Unless of course one of you
needs me to smile and wave.

10:00.968 --> 10:04.669
To the castle of
the two sisters.

10:04.671 --> 10:06.338
I'm not really
needed anywhere else.

10:06.340 --> 10:08.840
Might as well catch up
on some of my reading.

10:10.810 --> 10:12.010
Want some company?

10:12.012 --> 10:15.747
Applejack: It has been a while
since we've visited the castle.

10:15.749 --> 10:17.616
Might be fun.

10:17.618 --> 10:20.085
Maybe I could use a
little company right now.

10:22.888 --> 10:24.789
Rainbow dash: (sigh) I
still can't believe

10:24.791 --> 10:27.025
We had to give
back the elements.

10:27.027 --> 10:30.362
It had to be done or the tree of
harmony wouldn't have survived.

10:30.364 --> 10:36.167
Even without the elements, our
friendship is as strong as ever.

10:36.169 --> 10:38.703
I just hope another
"friend" of ours

10:38.705 --> 10:41.039
Never makes us sorry we
had to give them up.

10:41.041 --> 10:44.175
You're talking
about me, I presume?

10:45.077 --> 10:46.678
How'd you guess?

10:46.680 --> 10:48.013
My ears were burning.

10:48.015 --> 10:49.681
<i>(hiss)</i>

10:49.683 --> 10:52.384
What are you even
doing here, discord?

10:52.386 --> 10:54.953
Just a bit of light
reading before I head off

10:54.955 --> 10:57.255
On my extremely
important mission.

10:57.257 --> 10:59.290
I suppose you all know
that I've been tapped

10:59.292 --> 11:01.092
To capture a
certain escapee.

11:02.728 --> 11:04.029
Big deal.

11:04.031 --> 11:06.331
You're right, spike,
it is a "big deal".

11:08.868 --> 11:10.001
<i>(pop)</i>

11:10.003 --> 11:13.938
Seems I possess a magic that
gives me quite an important role

11:13.940 --> 11:18.176
Maybe they should make
me an alicorn princess.

11:18.178 --> 11:20.145
<i>(cheering crowd)</i>

11:20.147 --> 11:22.080
<i>(kisses)</i>

11:24.083 --> 11:25.684
In your dreams.

11:26.819 --> 11:29.187
Oh, I never dream
of such things.

11:29.189 --> 11:31.423
Ask princess luna.

11:31.425 --> 11:33.391
Don't you have a creepy
magic-stealing villain

11:33.393 --> 11:35.026
To track down?

11:35.028 --> 11:36.761
Yes, yes, yes, of course.

11:36.763 --> 11:40.265
It's just that I couldn't help
but notice that twilight

11:40.267 --> 11:43.435
Hasn't yet opened this
little chest of hers.

11:45.105 --> 11:49.307
What if what's locked inside is
something that could help her

11:49.309 --> 11:51.476
Prove her royal worth?

11:51.478 --> 11:54.312
I only bring it up because she
said that she'd been feeling

11:54.314 --> 11:57.716
Like her role as a princess
doesn't equate to much.

11:59.820 --> 12:02.987
How do you know how
she was feeling?

12:02.989 --> 12:06.324
Is eavesdropping not the way
you're supposed to find out

12:06.326 --> 12:07.992
What your best pals are up to?

12:07.994 --> 12:13.431
Will I ever learn the intricate
nuances of being a good friend?

12:16.470 --> 12:20.839
Well, in any case, I suppose
now is as good a time as any

12:20.841 --> 12:22.273
For me to make my exit.

12:24.143 --> 12:25.510
And good riddance!

12:25.512 --> 12:28.113
Oopsey doopsey,

12:28.115 --> 12:32.450
I almost left with the little
journal you've all been keeping.

12:32.452 --> 12:34.085
What a fascinating read.

12:34.087 --> 12:37.188
Haven't you girls
just learned so much?

12:37.190 --> 12:39.457
I've bookmarked a few of the
more interesting passages.

12:39.459 --> 12:41.826
You really should take a look.

12:42.962 --> 12:45.363
We're still on for tea later
aren't we, fluttershy?

12:45.365 --> 12:46.965
I wouldn't miss it.

12:48.100 --> 12:51.369
I'll bring the
cucumber sandwiches.

12:52.472 --> 12:57.375
Sometimes I think the "reformed"
discord is more obnoxious

12:57.377 --> 13:00.211
Than the "before he
was reformed" discord.

13:00.213 --> 13:03.481
But he could be
right, couldn't he?

13:03.483 --> 13:06.484
<i>What if there is something</i>
<i>important in that chest?</i>

13:09.488 --> 13:11.489
There's only one
way to find out.

13:19.031 --> 13:20.064
Anything?

13:20.066 --> 13:22.133
<i>(negative murmurs)</i>

13:22.135 --> 13:24.335
There must be something
in this library

13:24.337 --> 13:26.504
That can help me figure
out how to open it.

13:26.506 --> 13:28.406
The answer is in
one of these books.

13:28.408 --> 13:30.041
I just know it.

13:39.985 --> 13:43.354
<i>♪ (scary)</i>

13:43.356 --> 13:44.522
<i>(thud)</i>

13:44.524 --> 13:55.300
♪

13:55.302 --> 13:57.836
Tirek, I presume.

14:00.039 --> 14:01.372
Discord.

14:01.374 --> 14:03.007
You're free?

14:03.009 --> 14:05.043
As a bird.

14:05.045 --> 14:07.312
I commend you on
your escape.

14:08.280 --> 14:10.048
I'm afraid the
feeling isn't mutual.

14:10.050 --> 14:11.182
<i>(snap)</i>

14:16.155 --> 14:18.990
I should have known you would
want to have equestria

14:18.992 --> 14:20.425
All to yourself.

14:20.427 --> 14:22.060
Oh, I'm not doing
this for me.

14:22.062 --> 14:23.928
I'm doing it for my friends.

14:23.930 --> 14:27.065
Just between the two of us,
it's mostly for fluttershy.

14:27.067 --> 14:29.067
Fluttershy?

14:29.069 --> 14:31.102
You're not saying
you're friends with...

14:31.104 --> 14:32.537
Ponies!

14:32.539 --> 14:34.138
Surprise!

14:35.975 --> 14:39.978
I am surprised that someone with
your intellect does not see

14:39.980 --> 14:44.582
This "friendship" is but a
new form of imprisonment.

14:44.584 --> 14:47.185
Clearly you've had to
abandon your true nature

14:47.187 --> 14:49.354
To stay in their good graces.

14:49.356 --> 14:52.657
♪

14:52.659 --> 14:54.592
I have done nothing of the sort.

14:56.962 --> 15:00.164
Please. I've seen this before.

15:00.166 --> 15:02.500
But he was always weak-minded.

15:02.502 --> 15:04.202
You are discord.

15:04.204 --> 15:09.574
You cannot fall into the same
trap that claimed my brother.

15:09.576 --> 15:13.544
Help me to grow strong and be
rewarded with something

15:13.546 --> 15:18.683
Far greater than
friendship...Freedom.

15:20.686 --> 15:24.255
Once I have stripped these
ponies of their magic,

15:24.257 --> 15:26.557
Nothing would give
me greater pleasure

15:26.559 --> 15:30.395
Than to see their world
turned upside down.

15:30.397 --> 15:34.632
Who better to do so than the
master of chaos himself?

15:36.368 --> 15:41.039
Join me, discord, and
reclaim your greatness.

15:41.041 --> 15:44.175
Unless, of course,
"pony errand boy"

15:44.177 --> 15:48.046
Is the role you've always
wanted to play in this world.

15:55.187 --> 16:01.225
♪

16:01.227 --> 16:03.227
I think I've found something!

16:03.229 --> 16:05.263
I've been reading our journal
and there's something

16:05.265 --> 16:07.732
Interesting about the sections
that discord bookmarked.

16:07.734 --> 16:10.702
Applejack, do you remember
when you had to tell everypony

16:10.704 --> 16:13.004
That the tonic granny bought
from the flim-flam brothers

16:13.006 --> 16:14.372
Didn't really work?

16:14.374 --> 16:18.609
It was one of the hardest
things I ever had to do.

16:18.611 --> 16:20.211
<i>(gulping)</i>

16:25.417 --> 16:27.318
I hate to disappoint everypony,

16:27.320 --> 16:29.587
But there's no way granny
could have made that dive

16:29.589 --> 16:32.323
Because this tonic is a fake.

16:32.325 --> 16:33.725
<i>(gasp)</i>

16:33.727 --> 16:36.728
But in that moment, I
knew had to be honest.

16:36.730 --> 16:41.299
But what that's got to do
with opening the chest?

16:41.301 --> 16:44.035
I've found that each of you
has had to face a situation

16:44.037 --> 16:45.703
Where living up to the
element of harmony

16:45.705 --> 16:47.772
You represent wasn't easy.

16:47.774 --> 16:50.308
Fluttershy, it was when you
realized that the way to show

16:50.310 --> 16:53.444
Kindness to the breezies was by
forcing them to leave your home.

16:53.446 --> 16:56.047
<i>The looks on their</i>
<i>poor little faces.</i>

17:00.519 --> 17:02.754
<i>But I knew that as</i>
<i>difficult as it was,</i>

17:02.756 --> 17:06.124
Pushing them away was the
kindest thing I could do.

17:06.126 --> 17:09.360
Rarity, even after suri took
advantage of your generosity

17:09.362 --> 17:14.132
<i>You didn't let it cause you to</i>
<i>abandon your generous spirit.</i>

17:14.134 --> 17:15.767
I simply couldn't have
lived with myself

17:15.769 --> 17:17.802
If I didn't do something
special for the friends

17:17.804 --> 17:20.438
Who have always been
so generous to me.

17:20.440 --> 17:23.474
Rainbow dash, you had the chance
to fly with the wonderbolts

17:23.476 --> 17:25.243
At the equestria games

17:25.245 --> 17:27.578
But instead you chose to
compete with your friends.

17:27.580 --> 17:30.782
Sure. But being loyal to my
friends was way more important.

17:30.784 --> 17:35.620
Pinkie pie, you realized that
seeing your friend laugh

17:35.622 --> 17:38.222
Was more important than proving
you were a better party planner

17:38.224 --> 17:39.657
Than cheese sandwich.

17:39.659 --> 17:42.126
Best party I've ever had.

17:42.128 --> 17:45.096
It's clear we've all had our
moments to shine, twilight,

17:45.098 --> 17:46.431
But I'm with applejack.

17:46.433 --> 17:48.132
What does any of
this have to do

17:48.134 --> 17:49.667
With the opening of the chest?

17:49.669 --> 17:51.769
All of you had tough
choices to make,

17:51.771 --> 17:54.572
<i>But when you made the right</i>
<i>one and embraced your element,</i>

17:54.574 --> 17:57.542
<i>It helped somepony else</i>
<i>make the right choice too.</i>

17:57.544 --> 17:59.544
<i>Each of you received</i>
<i>something from the pony</i>

17:59.546 --> 18:01.846
<i>Whose life you helped change.</i>

18:01.848 --> 18:04.749
I know it sounds crazy, but
maybe there's something special

18:04.751 --> 18:07.085
About those objects that could
lead us to the location

18:07.087 --> 18:10.788
The chest is connected
to the tree of harmony.

18:10.790 --> 18:12.757
The tree is connected
to the elements,

18:12.759 --> 18:15.393
And the elements are
connected to all of us.

18:15.395 --> 18:17.428
There must be a connection!

18:17.430 --> 18:19.497
I hate to admit it,
but maybe discord

18:19.499 --> 18:21.632
Was trying to be a
good friend after all.

18:23.669 --> 18:26.404
I don't see anything on them
that would give us a clue

18:26.406 --> 18:28.306
As to where the keys might be.

18:28.308 --> 18:30.842
They're just ordinary,
everyday objects.

18:30.844 --> 18:32.343
Come on, boneless!

18:32.345 --> 18:33.878
Give us that key!

18:35.147 --> 18:36.714
I don't think that's
going to work.

18:37.816 --> 18:39.350
<i>(whoosh)</i>

18:39.352 --> 18:40.351
<i>(gasp)</i>

18:40.353 --> 18:45.389
<i>♪</i>

18:52.264 --> 18:55.133
<i>(whoosh)</i>

18:55.135 --> 19:04.842
♪

19:04.844 --> 19:06.777
There's still one key missing.

19:06.779 --> 19:09.180
The key that represents
the element of magic.

19:09.182 --> 19:10.748
My element.

19:10.750 --> 19:13.351
Oh, but I'm sure that if
we've gotten our keys,

19:13.353 --> 19:18.489
Think, twilight! When have you
completed a difficult magical

19:18.491 --> 19:22.627
Task and in doing so encouraged
another pony to do the same?

19:22.629 --> 19:26.564
If I had, I would have written
about it in the journal.

19:26.566 --> 19:30.201
Don't worry, twilight, I'm sure
you'll get your key eventually.

19:30.203 --> 19:32.603
<i>(retching)</i>

19:36.242 --> 19:39.477
That I'm needed in
canterlot at once.

19:39.479 --> 19:44.916
♪

19:44.918 --> 19:46.551
I came as quickly as I could.

19:46.553 --> 19:47.685
Is something wrong?

19:47.687 --> 19:51.656
I am afraid I put too
much trust in discord

19:51.658 --> 19:54.225
And the effect that friendship
would have upon him.

19:57.963 --> 20:00.531
<i>Discord has betrayed</i>
<i>the ponies of equestria</i>

20:00.533 --> 20:02.867
<i>And joined forces with tirek.</i>

20:02.869 --> 20:04.802
<i>(frightened gasps)</i>

20:08.207 --> 20:12.977
<i>(whoosh)</i>

20:19.752 --> 20:23.588
I thought our friendship
meant something to him.

20:23.590 --> 20:25.523
I thought he had changed.

20:25.525 --> 20:28.392
Tirek has stolen enough magic
that he now has the strength

20:28.394 --> 20:29.994
<i>To steal flight as well.</i>

20:33.999 --> 20:35.900
Without pegasi to
control the weather,

20:35.902 --> 20:38.302
<i>There will be no</i>
<i>rain in equestria.</i>

20:39.638 --> 20:42.306
<i>There is word he has gone</i>
<i>after earth ponies as well.</i>

20:45.345 --> 20:48.479
<i>They will not be able</i>
<i>to tend the land.</i>

20:51.483 --> 20:54.385
Ponies will no longer be
in control of their world.

20:54.387 --> 20:56.887
That power will
belong solely to tirek.

20:56.889 --> 21:00.558
There is no doubt that tirek
is after alicorn magic.

21:00.560 --> 21:02.460
With discord by his side,

21:02.462 --> 21:04.996
We will not be able to
stop him from taking it.

21:04.998 --> 21:10.768
His power will know no bounds
and all hope will be lost.

21:10.770 --> 21:13.371
But there is one solution.

21:14.740 --> 21:17.275
It is only by making
this sacrifice

21:17.277 --> 21:20.378
That equestria and the lands
beyond it might be saved.

21:21.913 --> 21:24.548
We must rid ourselves
of our magic

21:24.550 --> 21:27.485
Before tirek has the chance
to steal it from us.

21:27.487 --> 21:28.953
<i>(gasp)</i>

21:33.058 --> 21:35.393
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

21:37.629 --> 21:39.764
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

21:50.375 --> 21:52.543
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

21:52.545 --> 21:56.681
<i>♪ friends</i>
